data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Tierra del Este. This single-story residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and an array of desirable feature. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting ambiance. The highlight of the home is undoubtedly the large kitchen, offering an abundance of countertop space and a convenient center island. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a delightful dining room complete with built-in storage and a charming bar area. The home also offers multiple versatile living spaces perfect for creating a cozy haven for quality time with loved ones.
Centrally located, you'll have easy access to 375, numerous El Paso hospitals, and Fort Bliss. This home also has an assumable VA loan for qualified buyers. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience in Tierra del Este.
